= El CNH se disuelve

MÉXICO, D.F., diciembre de 1968 —

The Consejo Nacional de Huelga votes itself out of existence. The strike is over; the schools reopen under watch. Two hundred thousand students who learned to run a printing press, hold a brigade meeting, and outrun a granadero now have nowhere to take what they learned.

Some will go home. Some will go to the Party — warily; they remember who wasn't there. And some are already talking, very quietly, about the sierra.

- @reclutar: Open the doors wide. Youth sections, brigades, presses — let the comités walk in as comités.
- @filtrar: Recruit carefully, one by one. Half these assemblies have a DFS informer taking minutes.

@reclutar
