They come in with their own songs and their own contempt for your hierarchies, and the old cadres' meetings will never be quiet again. Somewhere in Gobernación, a filing cabinet gets a new drawer.

@filtrar
on-arrival: cnh_recruited = 2; members += 1; sup_students -= 3; guerrilla_meter += 5; expediente += 3

Careful, correct, cold. The ones you turn away do not stop being angry. A boy from the Poli — nineteen, a good speaker, brother beaten half to death on the second of October — shakes your organizer's hand politely and goes to look for people less careful.
